    <h1>Pinkas HaKehillot — Boryslaw Entry</h1>
    <p class="source-note">
      Source: Yad Vashem, <em>Pinkas HaKehillot Polin</em> (Encyclopedia of Jewish Communities in Poland),
      Boryslaw entry. Hebrew original OCR-translated to English.
      <strong>Drohobycz district, Lwów province.</strong>
    </p>

